nodes.text: Robert Nairne is a creature and droid performer that played Professor Allium in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, Cycyed Ock and Kullbee Sperado in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, Kaljach Sonmi and an unnamed alien in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi, and Hondo Ohnaka in portions of the Millennium Falcon: Smuggler's Run attraction.
